i\n| [[Uttarakhand]]<ref name=\"Uttaranchal\" /><sup>37</sup>\n| 12015/13/2010-B.C.II. 8 December 2011\n|\n|-\n|Jogi\n| [[West Bengal]]<ref name=\"West Bengal\" /><sup>28</sup>\n| 12011/88/98-BCC 6 December 1999\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"Andhra Pradesh\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/andhrapradesh.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Andhra Pradesh|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Assam\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/assam.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Assam|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Bihar\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/bihar.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Bihar|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Chandigarh\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/chandigarh.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Chandigarh|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Chhattisgarh\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/Chhattisgarh.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Chhattisgarh|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Daman and Diu\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/damananddiu.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Daman and Diu|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n \n<ref name=\"Delhi\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/delhi.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of N.C.T. Of Delhi|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Goa\">{{Cite web|url=http://ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/goa.pdf|title=Central list of OBCs for the state of Goa|publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes|accessdate=15 December 2